org.codice.ddf.registry.source.configuration

Class SourceConfigurationHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codice.ddf.registry.source.configuration.SourceConfigurationHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RegistrySourceConfiguration, org.osgi.service.event.EventHandler

    public class SourceConfigurationHandler
extends Object
implements org.osgi.service.event.EventHandler, RegistrySourceConfiguration
    This handler class is responsible for the create/update/delete of source configurations that come from registry nodes. It listens to the create/update/delete events to trigger its logic.
